data.description: Brick rambler with a nice large lot with a lot of backyard privacy hidden by privacy fence. Detached 2 car brick garage. Lots of parking, including a paved parking area at the back of the lot accessible from Orchard Drive. Central heat and air. New carpet, laminate flooring, paint, countertops and island. New casement windows in the living room. Wood burning fireplace insert can heat the house in a power emergency. Garage also includes a wood burning stove and is perfect for use as a detached workshop.
